Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.17,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kak Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:28.02,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Maaf, saya terlambat.\NTerima kasih sudah menungguku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.33,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tak apa, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.99,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku juga sedang asik baca buku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.86,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Sophia, kalau pakai seragam...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.32,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,berarti kamu belum kembali ke asrama\Nsetelah pelatihan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.84,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak... soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:48.14,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, pelatihan hari ini agak lama,\Njadinya tak sempat untuk kembali ke asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:52.93,flashback,VIKTOR,0,0,0,,Yosh! Yang selesai 100 putaran,\Nnambah 100 putaran lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:59.21,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kalau sudah semangat,\NKapten Volk memang tak bisa berhenti, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.27,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Rasanya dia seperti serigala sungguhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.92,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, pertama-tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.94,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,mau beli baju dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:08.59,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:13.85,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kalau pakek seragam... itu...\Nrasanya akan menarik perhatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:20.72,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Me-Memang benar.\NMisal ada anak akademi yang lihat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:26.90,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ah... benar juga, ya.\NMa-Maaf karena datang tanpa pikir panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:31.66,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak.\NLagi pula kalau tetap berpakaian begini, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:37.02,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kita bakal sulit berjalan sambil bergandengan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:38.10,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:42.05,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah! Maafkan!\NTiba-tiba aku bilang aneh-aneh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:44.05,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Saya juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:44.75,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:49.74,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Saya juga...\Ningin jalan-jalan... sambil bergandengan tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.26,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Di kamp pelatihan tempo hari... itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:02:00.20,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kita... tak punya banyak\Nkesempatan untuk berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:05.63,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Eh? Aku tiba-tiba ngomongin apa, sih?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:09.63,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ka-Kalau maumu juga begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.91,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku juga merasa senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:14.99,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.99,sign_TrebuchetMS,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&HB5ADFF&\3c&H897FE8&\shad0\pos(918,186.001)\fs112.5\fad(272,1)\fnBasic Comical NC\frz330.7}Imutnya!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.98,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,I-Imutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.68,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Hari ini aku ingin menghadiaimu sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:22.45,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.64,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Sejak kita menjadi kekasih...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:28.15,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,ini kan pertama kalinya\Nkita jalan bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.83,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.22,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:12.85,sign_Arial,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\b0\c&H131B11&\3c&HEEF2F4&\shad0\bord4.5\fs38.999\fscx86\fad(941,1)\pos(1215,191.999)}Gorilabirin yang Terang dan Gelap
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.21,main,SUBORDINATE 1,0,0,0,,Permisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.40,main,ERNST,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.40,main,SUBORDINATE 1,0,0,0,,Ba-Baru saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.38,main,SUBORDINATE 1,0,0,0,,Di distrik bangsawan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.42,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ba-Bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:02.75,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Apa... terlalu biasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.48,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Me-Memang benar,\Nsisi keamanannya kurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.82,main,SHOPWORKER,0,0,0,,Keamanan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.25,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak!\NBukan apa-apa, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.55,main,SHOPWORKER,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan yang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.50,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ya-Yang ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.36,main,SHOPWORKER,0,0,0,,Kakinya terlihat indah, loh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:29.52,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Bo-Bolehkah saya melihat\Ndesain lainnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.27,main,SHOPWORKER,0,0,0,,Cantiknya! Terlihat elegan sekali, loh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.47,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Be-Begitu, kah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.45,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Menurut Kakak bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.97,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kakak Senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.49,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah... menurutku... itu terlihat imut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.66,sign_Verdana,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\move(690,209.999,690,60.001)\c&H1B231F&\bord0\shad0\fs74.999\fad(1,271)}Wahyu Didapat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:51.34,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Di... Dia suka yang beginian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.64,main,SHOPWORKER,0,0,0,,Terima kasih telah belanja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:59.63,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas baju yang indah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.36,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kita pilih pakaian yang cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.23,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.19,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:27.90,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ya-Yang ini cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.84,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ternyata gaya rambut\Nmemang harus dicocokkan dengan pakaian kita, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.07,main,BOSS,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, lah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:33.77,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:38.34,main,BOSS,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, apa tak pernah ada\Nyang mengeluhkan selera fashionmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.67,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Be-Benar juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.09,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Memang ada...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.46,main,BOSS,0,0,0,,Gak heran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.14,main,BOSS,0,0,0,,Lebih rawat dirimu sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:47.95,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Siap laksanakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:48.94,main,BOSS,0,0,0,,Percantik dirimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.51,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.81,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kue di sini memang lezat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.26,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Hmm...\NBenar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.82,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Yang dingin-dingin juga enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.03,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:16.66,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Benar juga, Kakak ini tinggal sendiri, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.73,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.10,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aslinya rumahku itu\Ndulunya milik kerabatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.92,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku diizinkan tinggal,\Nsekalian untuk merawatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.85,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.62,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Jika bersedia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:31.27,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,setelah ini\Nbagaimana kalau ke rumahku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.05,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:37.29,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku kan belum pernah mengundangmu.\NJika kamu tak keberatan juga sih...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.71,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.56,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ke-Ke rumahnya Kak Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:47.07,sign_ArialBlack,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H1A1C1C&\3c&HB9A5A2&\shad0}Tinggal Sendiri\N{\alphaFF\t(1571,1738,\alpha00)} Rumah Pacar\N{\alphaFF\t(3115,3240,\alpha00)} Maksiat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.47,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ka-Kalau tiba-tiba gini...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:49.80,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Aku belum belum buat persiapan...\Ndan menguatkan mental...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.97,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kalau gak mau, tak apa tolak saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.39,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Niatku cuma ngajak makan malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.12,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Heh? Makan... malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:04.46,sign_TrebuchetMS,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\move(180,240.001,132,195.001,1,483)\an1\c&H1A1C1D&\3c&HC7CFD0&\shad0\frz9.855\fs38.999\fad(232,686)}Mengapa haluku sewadidaw ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.51,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Jika Kakak tak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.54,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya?\NKalau begitu, yuk kita beli bahannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.72,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Di dekat sini ada marché.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.63,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ma-Marché?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.18,main,ARCIENT,0,0,0,,Jadi, bagaimana kondisi Adipati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.02,main,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,Setidaknya ia berhasil selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.64,main,ARCIENT,0,0,0,,Begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:28.24,main,SHIN,0,0,0,,Kudengar pelaku\Nmengenakan kain merah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.99,main,GILBERT,0,0,0,,Benar, mereka memakainya\Ndi salah satu bagian tubuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.34,main,ERNST,0,0,0,,Itu artinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:38.76,top,ERNST,0,0,0,,{\b0\pos(1313.02,887.4)}{\fs56.25}Fajar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:38.76,main,ERNST,0,0,0,,Ini ulah Faksi Anti-Monarki, Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:43.92,main,VIKTOR,0,0,0,,Ada kemungkinan keterlibatan\Nbarang peledak seperti waktu itu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.04,main,VIKTOR,0,0,0,,Para kadet bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.71,main,ERNST,0,0,0,,Aku ingin hindari\Nkegaduhan yang tak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.34,main,ERNST,0,0,0,,Rahasiakan hingga\Nlebih banyak informasi masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:57.21,main,ERNST,0,0,0,,Sebelum jadi masalah besar,\Nkita harus hentikan pergerakan Akatsuki..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.82,main,VIKTOR,0,0,0,,Siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.69,main,ERNST,0,0,0,,Teruslah bersiaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:12.86,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Wah! Jadi ini marché?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.66,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Saya memang pernah dengar,\Ntapi baru kali ini datang langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:21.93,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Memang benar, siswa Dierentuin\Nmemang jarang datang ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.54,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.20,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Tomat ini terlihat lezat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:31.66,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Rasanya mereka jadi berkilau\Nkarena bermandikan cahaya mentari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.75,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Benar, mereka merah bagaikan rubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.82,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.47,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:46.90,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak. Malam ini\Nbagaimana kalau masak tomat saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.11,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Sepakat, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:57.78,main,WORM,0,0,0,,Hadeh, hari ini aku harus \Nkerja keras lagi. Lama-lama jadi berasa malas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.95,main,STINKBUG,0,0,0,,Hari ini ditugasi bangswan lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.83,main,WORM,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:06.58,main,STINKBUG,0,0,0,,Lagi pula memang ini nasib\Npenerima berkah Cacing dan Kutu Busuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:10.09,main,WORM,0,0,0,,Bagi orang penting,\Nnyawa mereka lebih penting dibanding berkahnya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:16.08,main,STINKBUG,0,0,0,,Ah, muak sekali.\NJalani hidup bergantung pada berkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.27,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aturan tak tertulis tentang berkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:26.64,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tak hanya di negeri kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.92,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,ini adalah masalah\Nyang dialami semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.46,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku ingin melakukan sesuatu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:37.92,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,tapi aku masih menjadi\NKadet Kesatria yang belum matang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.15,main,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,Abang di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:45.78,main,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,Beli kacang yang lezat ini, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.00,main,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,Aku kasih diskon, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:51.02,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Sa-Saya beli!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.22,main,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,Oh, makasih banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:01.33,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kita belanja banyak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.34,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:03.97,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.48,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:16.57,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Katanya sih rumah kecil,\Ntapi gede juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:17.94,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:21.02,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ke-Kenapa, Kak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:25.22,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku lupa beli bumbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.29,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,A-Aku mau beli dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:33.25,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Sophia, maaf.\NTapi masuklah dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.23,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.35,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ka-Kalau begitu, saya ikut saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:38.51,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak.\NSore begini di sana ramai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.56,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Lebih cepat kalau sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.29,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Gunakan kunci ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.43,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku segera balik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.01,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah, kunci itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.83,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,buatmu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.28,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.79,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Jadi... ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.06,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,artinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.08,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,kunci pasangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.97,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Saya permisi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:27.83,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Rumahnya indah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:33.70,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Bagian belakang...\Ndijadikan dapur, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.93,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Maaf aku lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.98,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tempatnya lebih ramai dari dugaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.50,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kakak, selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.64,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.64,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Saya pakai tanpa izin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.91,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku tak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:05.31,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Saya pikir untuk masak ini dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.46,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kamu terampil sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:09.88,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:15.02,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Aku juga mulai bisa\Nkendalikan batas kuasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.92,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ah, benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.43,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kakak mau icip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:27.85,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ah, kelepasan!\NTanpa mikir, aku acungkan sendoknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.27,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Hm, lezat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.04,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Be-Begitu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.04,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ta-Tak ada apa-apa kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.99,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Ah, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.01,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:20.51,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Ini kalung pemberian Kak Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.92,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kamu memakainya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.73,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:31.66,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Sejak saat itu selalu. Meski saat misi\Nsaya simpan karena takut hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:36.50,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Karena ini barang berharga\Nyang pertama kali diberikan Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.03,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:46.00,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Bisa dibilang, saya tak mau jauh darinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.36,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tak kusangka kamu berpikir begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.62,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:08.00,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya, aku khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:08.85,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.02,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:16.00,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,karena aku tak terpikir cara lain\Nselain memberikan hadiah agar kamu senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.29,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku cemas apa kamu suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.70,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,So... Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:28.03,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Sebelumnya kan aku pernah bilang,\Nkalau aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.97,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,mencintaimu, Kak Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:37.05,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Karena itu... anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:46.54,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Saya tak ingin Kakak...\Nmerasa cemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.73,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Maafkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:56.36,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Niatku bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.63,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Sophia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.30,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,I-Iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.31,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Sophia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:50.85,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,A-Anu... bukan begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.72,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Malam makin gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.37,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kamu harus segera bersiap pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.87,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Huh? Tapi kan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.83,sign_TrebuchetMS,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\move(960,135,960,90,1,360)\c&H1E242E&\bord0\shad0\gd40\fad(1,760)}Cubit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.62,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku antar, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.99,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Hari ini beristirahatlah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.55,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Te-Tentu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.40,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kak Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.77,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Yang tadi... maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:54.60,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tanpa pertimbangkan perasaanmu,\Naku mau maksa lanjut ke jenjang berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.23,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Aku sangat menyesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:01.85,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Bu-Bukan begitu.\NTadi itu... aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:05.07,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tak ada yang perlu\Nkamu mintai maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.25,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Karena itu...\Njangan berekspresi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:22.37,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Bukannya...\Naku menolak ajakan Kakak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:28.29,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Itu... hingga sekarang...\Naku belum punya pengalaman beginian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.99,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Aku hanya bingung...\Nbagaimana cara menanggapinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.95,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Setelah mendengar ini, aku jadi tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.23,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Tak apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.11,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kita tinggal maju sesuai kecepatan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:46.67,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:57.75,main,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Terima kasih telah mengantar hingga ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.58,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Bukan masalah, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.33,main,LOUIS,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, selamat malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.59,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Kak Louis itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:24.77,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,sadar kalau  aku takut...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:28.41,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,dan putuskan... untuk berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:53.78,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Aku telat banget.\NAku harus segera balik ke asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.39,main,KEITH,0,0,0,,Lah—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.06,main,LLOYD,0,0,0,,Dasar betina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:27.50,main,LLOYD,0,0,0,,Ternyata... dia emang ngeselin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.97,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Meski cuma sepontan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:46.48,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Sejak kapan aku jadi setangguh ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:54.10,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Po-Pokonya...\Naku tak bisa biarkan dua orang mencurigakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:57.92,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Pertama-tama...\Naku harus lapor  Ordo Kesatria...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.30,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Lohe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.24,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,Rasanya... kekuatanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.25,italics,SOPHIA,0,0,0,,tak mau keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.63,main,LEOHART,0,0,0,,Saat kamu paling bersinar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.53,main,LEOHART,0,0,0,,adalah saat bersamaku, loh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.71,main,LEOHART,0,0,0,,Sophia Riller.
